# SECURITY NOTES
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ⚠️  NEVER commit .env to version control
# ⚠️  Keep passwords secret and secure
# ⚠️  Rotate credentials periodically
# ⚠️  Use strong passwords (12+ characters, mixed case, numbers, symbols)

